properties.name: data
properties.description: use GoogleMapOverlays model class which is exported as part of library. It consist of latitude, longitude, title, show-title, icon & json object

properties.name: width
properties.description: Width for google map. value can be percentage of pixel

properties.name: initial-zoom-level
properties.description: User can provide zoom-level of map by default

properties.name: initial-lat
properties.description: Load map by default at latitude when loaded

properties.name: initial-lng
properties.description: Load map by default at longitude when loaded

events.name: onMarkerClick
events.description: It will fire on click of marker on google map
